1
00:00:00,533 --> 00:00:01,534
It's just acting.

2
00:00:01,534 --> 00:00:02,469
As long as it's believable.

3
00:00:02,469 --> 00:00:03,903
It's not.

4
00:00:04,971 --> 00:00:07,173
If you like someone, you should just say it.

5
00:00:09,309 --> 00:00:10,610
Maybe they're just afraid

6
00:00:10,877 --> 00:00:12,345
of losing the friendship.

7
00:00:12,879 --> 00:00:14,314
You'll never know if you don't ask.

8
00:00:15,715 --> 00:00:16,483
Maybe they just

9
00:00:17,617 --> 00:00:18,718
lack the confidence.

10
00:00:18,952 --> 00:00:20,086
They're just scared.

11
00:00:22,555 --> 00:00:24,190
What about you?

12
00:00:24,691 --> 00:00:26,025
How do you think

13
00:00:26,025 --> 00:00:27,060
your story would end?

14
00:00:29,262 --> 00:00:30,363
I'd just wish them well.

15
00:00:31,498 --> 00:00:33,199
Why can't you just say

16
00:00:33,767 --> 00:00:35,068
that you like them

17
00:00:35,068 --> 00:00:36,136
and want to be together?

18
00:00:36,569 --> 00:00:38,004
Because saying those things

19
00:00:38,471 --> 00:00:40,340
would just ruin the relationship.

20
00:00:55,588 --> 00:00:58,525
I know you wouldn't

21
00:00:58,525 --> 00:01:01,428
give your all for nothing.

22
00:01:02,128 --> 00:01:04,697
You just want to make up

23
00:01:04,697 --> 00:01:06,766
for all those past regrets.

24
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:10,203
Love is what keeps happiness

25
00:01:10,203 --> 00:01:13,273
from being cast aside.

26
00:01:15,008 --> 00:01:18,812
A happiness that's meant to be.

27
00:01:21,181 --> 00:01:22,248
That's a song I

28
00:01:22,649 --> 00:01:24,517
recently wrote for this show.

29
00:01:25,518 --> 00:01:26,019
By the way,

30
00:01:26,586 --> 00:01:27,320
do you ever

31
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,855
scroll past those

32
00:01:29,789 --> 00:01:31,391
really short songs online?

33
00:01:32,385 --> 00:01:33,453
They always sound so good, right?

34
00:01:34,561 --> 00:01:36,129
Do you know why that is?

35
00:01:36,563 --> 00:01:37,397
Why?

36
00:01:38,665 --> 00:01:40,333
Because those short clips

37
00:01:40,333 --> 00:01:42,135
are the best of the best.

38
00:01:42,135 --> 00:01:42,902
They're designed to

39
00:01:42,902 --> 00:01:44,504
grab your attention instantly.

40
00:01:45,371 --> 00:01:46,840
But the full versions

41
00:01:47,574 --> 00:01:48,908
need so much buildup

42
00:01:49,409 --> 00:01:50,810
that they're never as perfect.

43
00:01:57,650 --> 00:01:59,752
Why are you being so negative?

44
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:02,155
Did someone break your heart?

45
00:02:05,751 --> 00:02:07,920
You need to have more confidence.
